<item>
            <title>[HIVE-23868] Windowing function spec: support 0 preceeding/following</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-23868</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-12574&quot; title=&quot;windowing function returns incorrect result when the window size is larger than the partition size&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-12574&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-12574&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; removed support for 0 PRECEDING/FOLLOWING in window function specifications. We can restore support for this by converting 0 PRECEDING/FOLLOWING to CURRENT ROW in the query plan, which should be the same.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
