                            <comment id="17159548" author="jdere" created="Thu, 16 Jul 2020 23:17:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch to convert 0 preceeding/following to current row.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jcamachorodriguez&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jcamachorodriguez&quot;&gt;jcamachorodriguez&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17159549" author="jcamacho" created="Thu, 16 Jul 2020 23:18:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdere&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdere&quot;&gt;jdere&lt;/a&gt;, you will need to create a PR to trigger ptests with the new workflow.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17159553" author="jcamacho" created="Thu, 16 Jul 2020 23:24:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdere&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdere&quot;&gt;jdere&lt;/a&gt;, what do you think about adding the change to &lt;tt&gt;SelectClauseParser.g&lt;/tt&gt;? Maybe something like this would work?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
0 KW_PRECEDING -&amp;gt; ^(KW_CURRENT)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The reason I am asking is that then we will get CURRENT_ROW both through Hive and Calcite.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17159556" author="jdere" created="Thu, 16 Jul 2020 23:26:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;PR at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/pull/1269&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/hive/pull/1269&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17159558" author="jdere" created="Thu, 16 Jul 2020 23:27:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just saw your comment. Will take a look to see if the parser change is doable&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17159574" author="jcamacho" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2020 00:19:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdere&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdere&quot;&gt;jdere&lt;/a&gt;, nm, the path you changed is common for Hive and Calcite.&lt;/p&gt;

